<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1436,1511,1608]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,280,1511,1536]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Comments</emphasis>
. 
<bibRefCitation box="[294,440,1511,1536]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" refId="ref26892" refString="Hull, F. M. (1943 b) The New World species of the genus Baccha. Entomologica Americana, 23, 42 - 99, 10 pls." type="book chapter">Hull (1943b)</bibRefCitation>
originally named his species 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hull" authorityYear="1943" box="[774,963,1511,1536]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Baccha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cerberus">
<emphasis box="[774,963,1511,1536]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Baccha cerberus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but 
<bibRefCitation box="[1020,1286,1511,1536]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" refId="ref30666" refString="Thompson, F. C., Vockeroth, J. R. &amp; Sedman, Y. S. (1976) Family Syrphidae. A catalogue of the Diptera of the American South of the United States, 46, 1 - 195. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 49898" type="journal article">
Thompson 
<emphasis box="[1148,1197,1511,1536]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">et al</emphasis>
. (1976)
</bibRefCitation>
misspelled it as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Hull" baseAuthorityYear="1943" box="[182,291,1548,1573]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Ocyptamus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cereberus">
<emphasis box="[182,291,1548,1573]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">cereberus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This species was already related to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Hull" baseAuthorityYear="1943" box="[707,835,1548,1573]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Styxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="eblis">
<emphasis box="[707,835,1548,1573]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Styxia eblis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation box="[878,1024,1548,1573]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" refId="ref26892" refString="Hull, F. M. (1943 b) The New World species of the genus Baccha. Entomologica Americana, 23, 42 - 99, 10 pls." type="book chapter">Hull (1943b)</bibRefCitation>
in his original description and it fits the current diagnosis of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hull" authorityYear="1943" box="[421,488,1584,1607]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Styxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[421,488,1584,1607]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Styxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
